[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1545[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: an acute emergency surfaced mid-conversation is missed; a sensitive disclosure routes nowhere; a caregiver crisis is treated as a routine question. Continuous screening exists precisely because patients and caregivers do not telegraph emergencies on a separate channel; they raise them in the middle of a conversation about a referral, a medication, or a follow-up appointment.
