[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1643[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: the assistant discloses information the speaker is not authorized to see; the assistant ignores the patient's stated preferences; the assistant operates on stale or irrelevant context; the consent posture is not enforced. Speaker-role-driven scoping is the architectural primitive that turns "the assistant has the data" into "the assistant uses the data appropriately for who is in front of it."
