[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1647[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Step 6: Run the LLM-orchestrated conversation with citation discipline.** The conversation handler builds the system prompt with coordination context, scope rules, persona, and disclaimers. The user message plus recent context is the user input. The LLM, through Bedrock Agents, decides which tools to call, in which order, and synthesizes the result with citations to the coordination state, the protocol library, the patient-education library, and the provenance journal as appropriate.
