[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1907[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: ungrounded assertions reach patients; coordination instructions invent time windows that contradict institutional protocols; caregivers receive information the patient withheld from them; the assistant over-extends into clinical judgment. The output safety stage is where the assistant earns the right to be treated as a coordination tool rather than as a generic chatbot in a healthcare wrapper.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1908[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
