[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1910[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1911[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Step 8: Drive proactive engagement from care-event triggers and protocol cadences.** Many of the most valuable coordination touches are not initiated by the patient or caregiver. A post-discharge welcome-home check-in within forty-eight hours of a discharge ADT message; a referral-tracking follow-up a week after a referral order if no appointment has been scheduled; an appointment-prep nudge a few days before a visit; a missed-appointment outreach within twenty-four hours; a lab-result acknowledgement once the ordering clinician has signed off. Each is driven by the protocol library, not by the LLM.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1912[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1913[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1914[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ON proactive_engagement_due(patient_id, trigger):
