[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2010[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: the proactive cadence is missing; the patient-and-caregiver-preferences are ignored; quiet hours are violated; the proactive messages fail safety verification. Proactive engagement is where most of the assistant's coordination value materializes; the input the patient or caregiver gives in a synchronous chat is a small fraction of the total value.
