[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2013[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2014[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Step 9: Orchestrate transitions of care with explicit state machines.** When the patient transitions between care settings (hospital to home, hospital to skilled nursing, ED to primary-care follow-up, surgery to home), the assistant runs the institution's transition-of-care protocol as a Step Functions workflow. The workflow has explicit states, explicit transitions, and explicit completion criteria; the LLM operates on top of the workflow, not in place of it.
