[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2148[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: transitions of care are the highest-risk coordination events, and they are precisely where ad-hoc handling produces avoidable readmissions. Without the explicit state machine and the subscribed seam-detection, the most consequential window in the patient's care receives the least structured support.
