[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2151[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2152[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Step 10: Generate care-team reports and run the outcome-correlation pipeline.** The assistant's value to the care team materializes through structured reporting, not through the conversation surface. Real-time alerts for high-priority gaps, weekly digests, monthly summaries, transition-of-care closure reports, and quarterly clinical-review packets are first-class production scope. The outcome-correlation pipeline pulls subsequent claims and clinical data to measure whether the assistant's coordination touches translate into avoided utilization and improved patient experience.
