[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: the care team has no visibility into the assistant's activity; the assistant's value is invisible to the people who need to see it; the outcome demonstration is impossible; the per-cohort equity monitoring does not exist. Care-team reporting is how the assistant earns trust from the human care team, and the outcome-correlation pipeline is how the program earns its budget over time.
